to have -- this is a democracy.

00:30:01.600 --> 00:30:05.070
I also brought the one after
that, I am Sonja Sotomayor.

00:30:05.070 --> 00:30:07.550
So yeah, that's right.

00:30:07.550 --> 00:30:09.510
Let's see Sonja Sotomayor
do this.

